We have 3 people with epics so far in guild and continue to work more and more on epics. Many of us are just a few steps away. We love grouping and hunting together and helping one another. Usually you will find 2 or more of us together almost always and we all group together as often as possible. <br>
<br>
Requirements can be found <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://hoc.eq.tripod.com" target="top">here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> in the Guild Charter section but I'll give you a brief run over of them. You must be at least level 20. We are a good/neutral guild so if you are of an evil class or race you must meet certain criteria which is basically having good faction in 3 good cities. You must earn 5 votes from our members and attend 2 of our events. It is much easier to get your votes and enter the House in a weeks time if you attend one event first. <br>
<br>
We are currently recruiting all classes and races so if you are interested in joining a family fun environment I encourage you to take a look at the website and the message boards. Anyone wishing to be placed in the Quest of the Hopeful either contact myself or any of the other High Council (list can be found in Guild members section at the link above) in game and we will post you in the quest. <br>
<br>
We love inviting new people. We have just started a new recruiting push and are having a party to celebrate the newest 4 recruits from this week. I wish all future hopefuls good luck and I look forward to meeting and talking to you in-game.  <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=491453">Laennie Trueheart</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
