<br>
HoC is a family oriented guild.  the members of HoC, and the alumni live and die for each other.  every high level alumni of HoC that have gone off to other guilds still call HoC home, and are still a very big part of our lives.<br>
<br>
HoC is currently the oldest guild on Firiona Vie.  it was the third guild on this server.  the other two before it have disbanded.  as the oldest guild, our roots are deep, and our friendships and loyalty have withstood the test of time.<br>
<br>
i have never before felt more welcome anywhere.  i met a member of HoC as a lvl 2 necromancer in paineel.  i was hunting bats and baby skellies.  Ticlet, a lvl 52 necromancer was passing by from the Hole and said hello.  he mentored me for weeks.  we hunted together in the warrens nights on end as he taught me about my dark arts.  when i reached lvl 30, i started a new char on the server.  a cleric.  HoC was there for me every step of the way.  when both chars were lvl 31, i finally met the requirements to enter the guild.  <br>
<br>
the amount of time and energy sacrificed for me by the membership of HoC was incredible.  the integrity, honor, loyalty, honesty, and sincere friendships that the members of HoC possesse is second to none.   they exemplify a perfect house.<br>
<br>
i encourage everyone to browse the web site and read our ethos and mission.  to see what we stand for. as well read our goals section to see what we are working for and what we have achieved as individuals as well as a family of friends.<br>
<br>
a list of officers, as well as high council members is posted at the site.  please contact us in game or post on our boards if you are interested in becoming a part of something much bigger than yourself.  <br>
<br>
know that all are welcome with open arms.   <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=487255">Admire<br>
Sexy Necro</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <br>
